	<h1 class="title">NFL 在中国一直没火起来，阿里体育能帮上忙吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/102277/small/102277.jpg?1432868256" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">韩方航 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-08 11:53:57 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20442/medium/20442.jpg?1452224436" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


